---
title: Roasted Pork with Caramelized Apple and Cauliflower Mash
description: This dish is a simple supper of classic combinations — with a slight twist! See that creamy mash? It's actually a tasty combo of cauliflower and potato! Apple and pork is a delicious quintessential pairing and these caramelized apples are a cut above.
